action-platformer packed with legendary loot and stunning pixel art.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Collect an arsenal of powerful weapons and upgradeable skills, then use them to shoot and slash your way through hand-crafted pixel environments hiding a treasure trove of secrets.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Unravel a then use them to shoot and slash your way through hand-crafted pixel environments hiding a treasure trove of secrets.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Unravel a compelling story of regret and conspiracy as you slice your way through hordes of enemies and carry out your mission to save Calagan from total annihilation.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph"> Hybrid of action-platformer and looter<br/> Narrative-driven gameplay<br/> Collect an arsenal of mythic weapons<br/> Challenging enemies and intense boss class="css-1aq06d4-MarkdownHeading__heading">Foregone</h1><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Years after a devastating war, the city of Calagan is once again besieged by an all-corrupting force known as the Harrow.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">As the citys strongest super-soldier, its up to you to investigate the Harrows origins and prevent its reanimated minions from destroying your home. But the Harrow isnt just reviving the dead  its dredging up memories better left forgotten.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Foregone is a fast and fluid 2D action-platformer packed with legendary loot and stunning pixel art.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Collect an arsenal of powerful weapons and upgradeable skills, then use them to shoot and slash your way through hand-crafted pixel environments hiding a treasure trove of secrets.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Unravel a compelling story of regret and conspiracy as you slice your way through hordes of enemies and carry out your mission to save Calagan from total annihilation.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph"> Hybrid of action-platformer and looter<br/> Narrative-driven gameplay<br/> Collect an arsenal of mythic weapons<br/> Challenging enemies and intense boss fights<br/> Branching skill tree with customizable abilities<br/> Fluid 3D-to-2D pixel art &amp; animation </div></div><div class="css-138l5a7-ImageGrid-styles__grid" data-component="ImageGrid"><ul class="css-1aq06d4-MarkdownHeading__heading">Foregone</h1><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Years after a devastating war, the city of Calagan is once again besieged by an all-corrupting force known as the Harrow.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">As the citys strongest super-soldier, its up to you to investigate the Harrows origins and prevent its reanimated minions from destroying your home. But the Harrow isnt just reviving the dead  its dredging up memories better left forgotten.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Foregone is a fast and fluid 2D action-platformer packed with legendary loot and stunning pixel art.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Collect an arsenal of powerful weapons and upgradeable skills, then use them to shoot and slash your way through hand-crafted pixel environments hiding a treasure trove of secrets.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Unravel a compelling story of regret and conspiracy as you slice your way through hordes of enemies and carry out your mission to save Calagan from total annihilation.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph"> Hybrid of action-platformer and looter<br/> Narrative-driven gameplay<br/> Collect an arsenal of mythic weapons<br/> Challenging enemies and intense boss fights<br/> Branching skill tree with customizable abilities<br/> Fluid 3D-to-2D pixel art &amp; animation </div></div><div class="css-138l5a7-ImageGrid-styles__grid" data-component="ImageGrid"><ul But the Harrow isnt just reviving the dead  its dredging up memories better left forgotten.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Foregone is a fast and fluid 2D action-platformer packed with legendary loot and stunning pixel art.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Collect an arsenal of powerful weapons and upgradeable skills, then use them to shoot and slash your way through hand-crafted pixel environments hiding a treasure trove of secrets.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Unravel a compelling story of regret and conspiracy as you slice your way through hordes of enemies and carry out your mission to save Calagan from total annihilation.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph"> Hybrid of action-platformer and looter<br/> Narrative-driven gameplay<br/> Collect an arsenal of mythic weapons<br/> Challenging enemies and intense boss all-corrupting force known as the Harrow.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">As the citys strongest super-soldier, its up to you to investigate the Harrows origins and prevent its reanimated minions from destroying your home. But the Harrow isnt just reviving the dead  its dredging up memories better left forgotten.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Foregone is a fast and fluid 2D action-platformer packed with legendary loot and stunning pixel art.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Collect an arsenal of powerful weapons and upgradeable skills, then use them to shoot and slash your way through hand-crafted pixel environments hiding a treasure trove of secrets.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq" data-component="MarkdownParagraph">Unravel a compelling story of regret and conspiracy as you slice your way through hordes of enemies and carry out your mission to save Calagan from total annihilation.</div><div class="css-1chn1kq"
